text: Essarts-en-Bocage is a commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in the west of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2016 and consists of the former communes of Les Essarts (the seat), Boulogne, L'Oie and Sainte-Florence.Arrêté préfectoral 5 October 2015 == References == Category:2016 establishments in France Category:Communes in Vendée
title: Essarts-en-Bocage
